---
title: Hot Honey Chicken Sandwich with Lettuce & Pickled Cucumber | Serves 2
description: Here's a lunch that'll fill you with energy and satiate your cravings! This sandwich is packed with flavourful chicken, crunchy
salad and creamy aioli. If that wasn't enticing enough, the crowning glory to this meal is the homemade hot honey, adding
the perfect hit of sweet and spicy.
